data.name: description_bookmark1.Text
data.value: The operation of the Semi Autogenus Mill(SAG Mill) currently lacks standard references for the addition or reduction of water volume in the feed and discharge. The addition of water in the SAG Mill is crucial as it affects the fluctuations in power and millweight. Therefore, it is essential to regulate the water volume in the feed and discharge effectively. In this study, the author aims to apply the concept of fuzzy logic to the Semi Autogenous Mill as a guide for controlling the water volume in the SAG Mill. The utilization of a guide is expected to provide quantitative standards for companies in operating the SAG Mill regarding water addition. Currently, there are no standard references...
